                                    been responsive to our questions and incredibly helpful in getting us up and
                                    running.<%= image_tag("icons/quote02.svg", class: 'bottom') %></p>

                                <div class="info">

                                    <div class="text">
                                        <h4>Jeremy Heil</h4>
                                        <span>Digital and Private Records Archivist at Queen’s University
                                            Archives</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Crowd Testimonials End -->

    <!-- Crowd Logos -->
    <section class="crowd-logos">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="title">Our software has been trusted by librarians and archivists at these institutions:</h2>

            <%= image_tag("materials/transcription-archive-logos.png") %>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Crowd Logos End -->

    <!-- Crowd Banner -->
    <section class="crowd-banner">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="item">
                        <h4>Designed for Special Collections & archive’s unique needs</h4>
                        <p>Helping archivists to transcribe and create searchable resources with ease</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="item">
                        <h4>No Long Learning Curves</h4>
                        <p>Easy-to-use project owners’ interface and transcribers just type what appears in the sources
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="item">
                        <h4>Simple controls</h4>
                        <p>Tools to manage public or private transcriber teams</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="item">
                        <h4>Preserve Your Time </h4>
                        <p>Collaborators choose their work and review workflows are built in</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Crowd Banner End -->

    <!-- Crowd Testimonials -->
    <section class="crowd-testimonials mt100">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="second-title">
