                        <li>For every client we start by diving deep on your particular materials with you to talk
                            through optimal transcription strategies and set-up.</li>
                        <li>It’s as easy as adding digitized documents to FromThePage and inviting your community to
                            help transcribe those materials.</li>
                        <li>We present an image of the uploaded page to a user and a place for them to type what's on
                            the page. Those two things together make magic, but the magic is done by humans.</li>
                        <li>No need to wonder if our software can measure up to your unique holdings, we are happy to
